Model

Class Peashooter

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Piece
      • Model.Peashooter

  • public class Peashooter
extends Piece
    The Peashooter class provides the PlantsVSZombie game with a single Piece type that once called can create a Peashooter Piece in of itself. This class only contains a constructor and simplifies the Piece class code. It uses its super class Piece to create a new object and passes it's designated parameters.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    RG
